snippet: Tiger Woods shot a nine-under-par 63 on Friday to trim a six-shot deficit to one after the second round of the Turkish Open in Belek.
abstract: Tiger Woods trims six-shot deficit to one following second round of the Turkish Open in Belek, trailing leading foursome; other golf news noted.
